        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Pui Pui Protected Forest (red frame) with collecting sites of Pristimantis sinschi sp. nov. (yellow symbols) and P. albertus and P. sagittulus (blue symbol). Modified after Lehr et al. (2017)." , "Figure 9. Colouration in life variation of males of Pristimantis albertus A, B (MUSM 31956, SVL 13.7 mm) C, D (IWU 257, SVL 13.4 mm) E, F (MUSM 31959, SVL 12.9 mm). Photos by E. Lehr." , "Figure 8. Life colouration of female (A-D, IWU 237, SVL 24.2 mm) and male (E-H, NMP-P 6 V 75067, SVL 15.5 mm) Pristimantis albertus in dorsolateral (A, E), dorsal (B, F), ventral C, G) and lateral (D, H) views. Photos by E. Lehr." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/476514" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/476520" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/476519" .

